data.text:
Dragonfly Hollow

Update for Former Guests: the stone house and yard are no longer part of our spot. ***See the last photo in our gallery for an overview map of the updated Sniffspot. Please park at the top of the hill by the large metal barn and walk down the hill on the path on the right to the pond. We are open occasional hours due to surveying and construction soon to be started. Please message me if you have a specific time you want to come out and I will open for you if possible! Dogs can run, swim, play and explore the 18 acres of fields above our farm pond. Seating, water and lots of parking. We are only 3 miles from the Baltimore Beltway, 12 miles from the Inner Harbor! We are adjacent to a local pick your own peaches, apples and berry farm.

Unfenced

8 acres

5( 460 )

$18 dog / hour

Glen Arm, MD

The Blue House Play Park

Welcome to the Blue House Play Park! Easy to find and convenient entrance to the backyard right in front of the driveway. Feel free to park on the drive or in front of the house if parking is available, or anywhere you see fit in the cul-de-sac. You will have uninterrupted time with your pup(s) in my large fenced-in backyard. I have one doggo but won't be outside during your booked time. Feel free to use the hose for water and the trash can to dispose of waste. I have a container of dog toys available for use, as well as added agility equipment for those who wish to do a little training. The grass in the yard is cut every two weeks during the summer leading into the fall months. There may be some divots/holes in the yard so please watch your footing.

Fully Fenced

Tiffani's Private Dog Park In Dundalk

Spot ON HOLD temporarily for lawn regeneration, REOPENING April 1. Does your dog love to swim or run? Does your dog need a friendly labrador playmate? Individual or group play available at this fully fenced, 0.75 acre property with dock and ramp access to Bear Creek. Lots of space to run and play on grass. Trees and porches provide shade. Chickens in a small coop and resident Labrador on site. May make reservations for group or individual play, with or without friendly resident dog.

Fully Fenced

Daisy's Digs

We can't wait to host you and your pup(s) at our fully fenced, private pup oasis! Come and let your pup run free with no worries of escape! We provide toys, bug spray, and plenty of water for your pup! If it's a hot day- no worries! We have a kiddie pool (by request)and doggie towels so your pup can cool off! For our two-legged friends, take this time to relax at the umbrella table, or request to use our hammock or hammock swing and relax while your pup plays!

Fully Fenced

0.25 acres

Westminster, MD

Seeley Family Friendly Dog Park In Glen Burnie

Thanks for stopping by! We have a large fenced in backyard, great for your pet's playtime or puppy play dates! More than enough room for a dozen dogs! Our patio features a gazebo WITH overhead fan. Plenty of shade during the warmer months and a fire pit offers some extra warmth during the cooler months. During the summer season, Extras such as a puppy pool, Lounge Pool for Humans and sprinklers will be made available! Amenities: Snacks, Bottled Waters, and Poop Bags are always included. Wifi is available as well. We are a smoke friendly yard - lighter and ashtray are located on the patio table. Please dispose of all waste in the trashcan. Seating: We have 4 Chairs under the gazebo. We also have 5 other lounge chairs available in the yard. Parking: Our driveway can accommodate 7-9 vehicles. Street Parking is also available. If using the driveway, please pull far enough in to allow other vehicles to enter/exit.

Fully Fenced

Jenna's Fully Fenced Private Dog Park in Rockville

Welcome to our Rockville spot! A large yard with lots of room for you and your pup to sniff and play! Please enter through the wooden gate on the right hand side of the house. Let me know if you have any issues at all :)
